      / SERIAL DISK OVER THE CONSOLE PORT (SYS)                           Page 2


   30 00000* 7400  BTWC,   -0400           /WORD COUNT TO TRANSFER 
   31 00001* 0001  BTCA,   0001            /CURRENT ADDRESS TO STORE WORD.
   32 00002* 0000  BTTMP,  .-.             /THIS IS AN INITIAL DONT CARE VALUE.
   33              
   34              / THE NEXT FOUR WORDS REPLACE THE PATCH CODE IN THE BOOT2 HELP LOADER
   35 00003* 7605  OS8GO,  7605            /OS8 ENTRY POINT
   36 00004* 0047  BTSRC,  0047
   37 00005* 7647  BTDST1, 7647
   38 00006* 7600  BTDST2, 7600
   39              
   40 00007* 6031  BOOT2,  KSF             /GET A CHARACTER FROM SERIAL DISK SERVER
   41 00010* 5007          JMP .-1
   42 00011* 6036          KRB
   43 00012* 7006          RTL             /LEFT SHIFT 4 BITS TO BUILD UPPER HALF
   44 00013* 7006          RTL
   45 00014* 3002          DCA BTTMP       /SAVE FOR COMBINE
   46 00015* 6031          KSF             /GET LOWER 6 BITS
   47 00016* 5015          JMP .-1
   48 00017* 6036          KRB
   49 00020* 1002          TAD BTTMP
   50 00021* 3401          DCA I BTCA      /STORE THE WORD IN MEMORY
   51 00022* 2001          ISZ BTCA        /POINT AT NEXT ADDRESS
   52 00023* 2000          ISZ BTWC        /SKIP IF DONE
   53 00024* 5007          JMP BOOT2       /GO DO THE NEXT WORD
   54              
   55              / WHEN WE GET HERE THE BOOT BLOCK IS LOADED IN MEM PAGES 0 AND 1
   56              / WE NOW NEED TO COPY THEM INTO PLACE.
   57              
   58              / FIRST DO THE FIELD 1 PIECE
   59 00025* 1404  BTCPY1, TAD I BTSRC     /LOAD
   60 00026* 6211          CDF 10          /SWITCH TO FIELD 1
   61 00027* 3405          DCA I BTDST1    /STORE
   62 00030* 6201          CDF 00          /SWITCH TO FIELD 0
   63 00031* 2004          ISZ BTSRC       /BUMP SRC ADDRESS WILL NEVER SKIP
   64 00032* 2005          ISZ BTDST1      /BUMP DST ADDRESS AND SKIP IF DONE
   65 00033* 5025          JMP BTCPY1
   66              
   67              / NEXT DO THE FIELD 0 PIECE
   68 00034* 1404  BTCPY2, TAD I BTSRC     /LOAD
   69 00035* 3406          DCA I BTDST2    /STORE
   70 00036* 2004          ISZ BTSRC       /BUMP SRC ADDRESS WILL NEVER SKIP
   71 00037* 2006          ISZ BTDST2      /BUMP DST ADDRESS AND SKIP IF DONE
   72 00040* 5034          JMP BTCPY2
   73              
   74 00041* 5403          JMP I OS8GO     /AND GO START OS8
   75              
   76 00042* 0000          ZBLOCK 047-.    /PAD TO FILL THE SECTION
